parameters.description:
### Banner ID
Returns all term enrollment base records for the Banner ID passed.
```
/student-term-enrollment-bases?criteria={"bannerId":"300444500"}
```
### Term
Returns all term enrollment base records for the term code passed.
```
/student-term-enrollment-bases?criteria={"termCode":"201010"}}
```
### Enrollment Status
Returns all term enrollment base records for the enrollment status code passed.
```
/student-term-enrollment-bases?criteria={"enrollmentStatusCode":"EL"}
```
### Enrollment Status Date
Returns all term enrollment base records based on the enrollment status date passed. Equal to (:), less than ($lt), less than or equal to ($lte), greater than ($gt), and greater than or equal to ($gte) supported. 
```
/student-term-enrollment-bases?criteria={"enrollmentStatusDate":"2023-05-03"}

/student-term-enrollment-bases?criteria={"enrollmentStatusDate":{"$lt": "2023-05-03"}}

/student-term-enrollment-bases?criteria={"enrollmentStatusDate":{"$lte": "2023-05-03"}}

/student-term-enrollment-bases?criteria={"enrollmentStatusDate":{"$gt": "2023-05-03"}}

/student-term-enrollment-bases?criteria={"enrollmentStatusDate":{"$gte": "2023-05-03"}}
```
### Registration Reason
Returns all term enrollment base records for the registration reason code passed.
```
/student-term-enrollment-bases?criteria={"registrationReasonCode":"CE"}
```
### Minimum Registration Hours
Returns all term enrollment base records for the minimum registration hours passed. Equal to (:), less than ($lt), less than or equal to ($lte), greater than ($gt), and greater than or equal to ($gte) supported. 
```
/student-term-enrollment-bases?criteria={"minimumRegistrationHours":12}

/student-term-enrollment-bases?criteria={"minimumRegistrationHours":{"$lt":12}}

/student-term-enrollment-bases?criteria={"minimumRegistrationHours":{"$lte":12}}

/student-term-enrollment-bases?criteria={"minimumRegistrationHours":{"$gt":12}}

/student-term-enrollment-bases?criteria={"minimumRegistrationHours":{"$gte":12}}
```
### Minimum Registration Hours Source Code
Returns all term enrollment base records for the minimum registration hours source code passed.
```
/student-term-enrollment-bases?criteria={"minimumHoursSourceCode":"USER"}
```
### Maximum Registration Hours
Returns all term enrollment base records for the maximum registration hours passed. Equal to (:), less than ($lt), less than or equal to ($lte), greater than ($gt), and greater than or equal to ($gte) supported. 
```
/student-term-enrollment-bases?criteria={"maximumRegistrationHours":18}

/student-term-enrollment-bases?criteria={"maximumRegistrationHours":{"$lt":18}}

/student-term-enrollment-bases?criteria={"maximumRegistrationHours":{"$lte":18}}

/student-term-enrollment-bases?criteria={"maximumRegistrationHours":{"$gt":18}}

/student-term-enrollment-bases?criteria={"maximumRegistrationHours":{"$gte":18}}
```
### Maximum Registration Hours Source Code
Returns all term enrollment base records for the maximum registration hours source code passed.
```
/student-term-enrollment-bases?criteria={"maximumHoursSourceCode":"MHRS"}
```
### Charges Acceptance Indicator
Returns all term enrollment base records for the charges acceptance indicator passed. Valid values are 'C' for Confirmed, for 'N' for None, or 'Y' for Accepted.
```
/student-term-enrollment-bases?criteria={"chargesAcceptanceInd":"N"}
```
### Current Time Status Code
Returns all term enrollment base records for the current time status code passed.
```
/student-term-enrollment-bases?criteria={"currentTimeStatusCode":"HT"}
```

